Morrison Knudsen Corp said a unitwas awarded an 11-1/2-year contract totaling about 200 mln dlrsfor the operation of a steam coal mine near Montgomery, W.Va.    The company said the contract carries an option for anadditional 10 years.    Of the 200 mln dlrs, the company said that only the firstfive years, or about 90 mln dlrs, were included in its firstquarter backlog.    The contract was awarded by &lt;Cannelton Industries Inc>, thecompany said. Reuter&#3;